{"type": "article", "id": 14940, "title": "26 个关于地域的误解，你的家乡躺枪了吗？| 每天还有一个 List", "description": "我都不知道这些误解是怎么发生的，幼小的心灵就受到了伤害。", "date": "2015-10-03T08:45:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16064, "name": "误解"}], "category": 5, "author": 112725, "comment_count": 105, "praise_count": 203, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104735FRdxVCElDec17k3P.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>1 东北人都不怕冷，都特能喝酒，都会唱二人转，都爱吃酸菜、穿花袄。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104634CKWSbl40wenGyf6i.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.59876543\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>2 北方人从不吃米饭，天天吃馒头。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104635A514320dhzotUrVv.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>3 北京考生 400 分上清华北大。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104635qUYZyiR1mczOwHlP.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>4 河南人都是骗子。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104636D1TMxa3Kto0A4Qgr.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>5 宁夏人都是骑骆驼上学。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104637YXgrKcNeCilkzJwo.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56206089\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>6 山西人都是开煤矿的，土大款。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104700krTt8KG5s4cxD130.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>7 山东人天天煎饼卷大葱。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104701npBXhqNLY08mur1b.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.73875803\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8 枣庄都是枣！</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104704bBOWTuXfeRt6GwM7.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.59777778\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9 兰州是沙漠，考试考打狼，只吃兰州拉面。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104705AligdUru7tZJDIBT.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10 内蒙古人渴了只喝牛奶，骑马上学，住蒙古包，学习的是骑马射箭。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104705LNT7PXq2uOcazfH3.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.814\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11 新疆人都是坏蛋，卖切糕。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104713DYwZr3e8KtxzFNXE.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"1.19008264\" data-format=\"GIF\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>12 南方人很矮。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104720yXsQqCYcuOte2NhL.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>13 温州人都是老板。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104721Vs3Tu69qi1jwEUce.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.45381526\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14 舟山人人有一座岛。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071047224kGbPBEdNAIHFTxh.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.54108216\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>15 长沙人，天天吃臭豆腐、天天参加快乐大本营。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104723N4p1jfePFhduyziK.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.546\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>16 江西人都是老表。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104724vJkRKdryglAbPBpS.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.61777778\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>17 江苏人都是学霸。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104725eg1b7vYKENjVySIH.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.57333333\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18 贵州人上街都带刀，还会下蛊。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104727e3GiYQD84r2TglVP.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.428\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19 上海人特别没种还老搞歧视，男的都小气且娘，女的都很作。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104728cmIbTMrfysJLvo5h.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.56145251\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>20 论《胡建人怎么学习普通发》</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104729BVqnl6ejdrc4KPU0.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.576\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>21 四川人没事儿吃花椒玩，喝的水都是辣的。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104729lsHjgycK5OXvwi7h.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.762\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>22 广东人，吃老鼠吧，还有小孩儿什么的，不然怎么会叫煲仔饭！</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104730eJV8EMX0xfij2W4z.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.538\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>23 云南人骑大象上学，到处都载歌载舞，炒菜放毒品。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104731amKnyI1O9J3HEt5s.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.52\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>24 玉林人一日三餐都是吃狗肉。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071047328pKuP3VSTeDWF9Zr.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.76335878\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<strong>25 海南人都会游泳。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104732yiaWd53o2gt0Gpe4.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>26 东莞人，我不想多说了。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607104735nW2HFyr0ua17q3Yb.gif\" title=\"1\" alt=\"1\" data-ratio=\"0.65306122\" data-format=\"gif\"></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}